nd mixed reality training tool specifically engineered for basketball players looking to improve their ability to make spilt-second decisions. Enhance your cognitive skills like never before by mastering offensive principles such as: attacking the top foot, assessing a closeout, splitting-the-screen, rolling off the inside shoulder, knowing when to euro step, and much more. Get the mental and physical reps needed to build true self-confidence while immersing yourself in the future of film study and player-development.\ud83d\udcc8\n\nSEE QUICK and REACT FAST with interactive drills focused on\ud83d\udcaa: \n\no\tChange-Of-Pace\no\tChange-Of-Direction\no\tFootwork\no\tBalance\no\tFluidity\no\tRhythm\no\tHand/ Eye Coordination\no\tAgility\no\tStrength and Conditioning\no\tCreating Space/ Separation\n\nMAKE YOUR MIND SWEAT with signature exercises designed for\ud83e\udde0:\n\no\tDecision-Making\no\tReaction Time\no\tPattern Recognition\no\tAttention Shifting\no\tMulti-Tasking\no\tAnticipation\no\tInhibition\no\tVisual Processing\no\tProblem-Solving\no\tProprioception\n\nSay goodbye to plastic cones, chairs, and trashcans.\ud83d\udeab\n\nREAL WORKOUTS. UNREAL DECISIONS.\ud83c\udfc0\ud83c\udfc6 #QourtVisionXR", "short_description": "Requiring a real ball to play, Qourt Vision XR trains cognitive skills such as decision making, reaction time, anticipation, hand/ eye coordination, pattern recognition, and more through real in-game simulations for the ultimate interactive basketball workout. For more information visit us at: https://www.handlefitness.com"}]}, "developer_name": "Handle Fitness", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.handlefitness.com/faq", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "RCM Productions, Inc.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.handlefitness.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topi